{"tid":1155535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(文明大會) 習近平：中国是亞洲和世界的中国　必然更開放擁抱世界","createTime":"2019-05-15T04:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T05:26:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9df2f2955a98e1fec39be6997226ef5d52db77c3","tid":1155535,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:20:42.000Z","msg":"亞洲文明對話大會早上在北京開幕，國家主席習近平發表主旨演講。他說如果各國重新回到自我封閉的孤島，人類文明將因老死不相往來而失去生機活力，及亞洲人民期待開放融通的亞洲。<br />\n<br />\n習近平又說，亞洲近幾十年發展，經驗之談是要趟開大門，主動融入世界經濟發展潮流，相信亞洲人民亦想遠離封閉，希望各國秉持開放精神，推進政策溝通、實施聯通、貿易暢通、資金融通、民心相通，共同構建亞洲和人類文明共同體。<br />\n<br />\n他提出四點主張，堅持相互尊重、平等相待，認為人類只有膚色語言之別，文明只有姹紫嫣紅之別，但絕無高低優劣之分。認為自己的人種和文明高人一等，執意改造甚至取代其他文明，在認識上是愚蠢的，在做法上是災難性，應該秉持平等和尊重，摒棄傲慢和偏見，加深文明差異性的認知，推動不同文明交流對話、和諧共生。他又說，要堅持交流、包容、互學互鑒，才有創新發展。<br />\n<br />\n習近平強調，今日中國，不僅是中國的中國，而是亞洲和世界的中國，未來的中國必然會以更開放的姿態擁抱世界，以更有活力的文明、成就貢獻世界，中國願與各國開展平等對話和交流，認為今次舉辦文明對話大會，是為相互啟迪提供新的平台。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457620-20190515.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457620-20190515.htm&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV%2BCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=19bbfb37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457620-20190515.htm&h=665b046b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457620-20190515.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6dc1c72f68fb3cfb52ffef058e2f364b8ac7ae91","tid":1155535,"uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:21:30.000Z","msg":"讀錯<br />\n<br />\n亞洲和世界是中国的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6158429f2f1e5e34a13f25c8f4d4fca54b961335","tid":1155535,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/sketch-1520247857707.png?fit=1200%2C675\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fsketch-1520247857707.png%3Ffit%3D1200%252C675&h=243566cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181101/7214bbdec354454b9190fa1b58144ee9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20181101%2F7214bbdec354454b9190fa1b58144ee9.jpeg&h=3a316f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181017/5a5b2fd11619444aaa4d62ca54322f3a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20181017%2F5a5b2fd11619444aaa4d62ca54322f3a.jpeg&h=bbce85c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2321350bb54e55e48e69145160d4077e54dca37d","tid":1155535,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"文明??!"},{"pid":"d543eb1a6d42403c4ead14b29590afce56f3f825","tid":1155535,"uid":100276,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"支那封完whatapp未"},{"pid":"caaeaea672d42ce2ad5c7036de47c48f6af66b7d","tid":1155535,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"上年改革開放幾多周年話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想開放多幾多年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396b34f53317978f0e64335581f01fb2bc0968e8","tid":1155535,"uid":202139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:29:08.000Z","msg":"談，可以！ <br />\n打，奉陪！ <br />\n欺，妄想！"},{"pid":"cd17d36f857b3bf1a8f1c3d83f5da89c76db9892","tid":1155535,"uid":31405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"支那講人學文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c148e4e9a525ab40a03c92ff464317feec3c0f","tid":1155535,"uid":94819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4811bbcf8e22b923f90e6f1d08e496a4b66cedf0","tid":1155535,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"不懂普通話就無人權係邊個國家講既？"},{"pid":"af791982e8df86c11da0b98f09a3403ea0492aa6","tid":1155535,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"中國外交官：不懂普通話 談何人權？<br />\n<br />\n美國之音18日報導，中國一名外交官近日在為新疆拘禁營辯護時暗示，如果一個人不掌握普通話等技能，那他就沒有人權可言。<br />\n報導指出，中國官方的《環球時報》16日以「大使講述新疆真相」為題，報導了中國駐哈薩克大使張霄與哈薩克媒體的訪談錄。<br />\n面對哈薩克多家媒體的鏡頭，中國駐哈薩克大使張霄再度重申中國官方立場：新疆根本不存在所謂「集中營」或「古拉格」，只有「職業技能培訓中心」。<br />\n張霄說，這些「培訓中心不是監獄，而是面向全社會的學校」，目的只有一個，「就是把人教育好，不讓好人變壞人」。<br />\n至於如何成為「好人」，張霄認為，首先要學習國家通用語言和文字，即普通話。<br />\n張霄說：「說到人權，試問一個現代人，如果不會讀寫本國通用語言文字 &hellip;&hellip;還有什麼其他人權可言？！」<br />\n據估計，新疆至少把100萬名維吾爾人及穆斯林關押進所謂的「再教育營」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e93d6b1712fac9abb72fa860ba89c958ee8480","tid":1155535,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"文明只有姹紫嫣紅之別，但絕無高低優劣之分<br />\n點會無分呀又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f50ec742247e5918de9d50c53b5b9d44587485","tid":1155535,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"開放精神？睇吓網禁先啦on99"},{"pid":"7787eff0f7ba52c36f6adf6fb708fd2f3fd2014b","tid":1155535,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"驅喇嘛毀經旗 中国進一步打壓藏傳佛教<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1155328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1155328</a>"},{"pid":"e0559276278943565a8dbe86a6878287f8ee8f4b","tid":1155535,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T04:56:29.000Z","msg":"習近平強調，今日中國，不僅是中國的中國，而是亞洲和世界的中國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亞洲？唔係宇宙咩